  "id": "did:web:etzhayyim.com:noroshi",
  "name": "noroshi",
  "displayName": "烽 — Photonics-Electronics Convergence (光電融合) Communication Chip + ISAC + Photonic Packaging Robotics",
  "displayNameJa": "烽 (のろし / 狼煙)",
  "displayNameEn": "Noroshi",
  "description": "The photonics-electronics convergence (光電融合) communication-chip actor: the silicon-photonic / co-packaged-optics (CPO) sibling of the electronic silicon/iwakura/fuigo line and the RF tsutae comms device. 烽 (狼煙, beacon-fire) is the original optical telecom — a watchtower SENSES a distant fire and RELAYS a coded message, one emission with two functions, which is exactly ISAC (Integrated Sensing And Communication). Three faces: (chip) design + link-budget of photonic-IC / CPO communication chips on open photonic-EDA; (isac) an OFDM-JCAS simulator doing communication capacity AND range-Doppler sensing from one waveform; (packaging) photonic assembly robotics (fibre↔grating active alignment, photonic wire-bonding) under a laser-safety interlock. CIVILIAN by construction: weaponisation is structurally unrepresentable (N1), ISAC senses objects not persons (N2), EPDA is clean-room open-source only (N5).",
  "descriptionJa": "光電融合の通信チップ actor。電子系の silicon/iwakura/fuigo 系列と RF の tsutae 通信デバイスの、シリコンフォトニクス / 光電パッケージ実装 (CPO) 版の兄弟。烽 (狼煙) は古来の光通信そのもの — 望楼が遠方の火を *感知* し符号化した報を *伝達* する、1 つの放射で 2 機能、これがまさに ISAC (Integrated Sensing And Communication)。3 つの face: (chip) open な photonic-EDA 上での photonic-IC / CPO 通信チップ設計 + リンクバジェット; (isac) 1 波形から通信容量 *と* レンジ-ドップラ センシングの両方を行う OFDM-JCAS シミュレータ; (packaging) レーザ安全インターロック下での光実装ロボティクス (ファイバ↔グレーティング能動整列, photonic wire-bonding)。構造的に民生限定: 兵器化は表現不能 (N1)、ISAC は人ではなく物体を感知 (N2)、EPDA は clean-room open-source のみ (N5)。",
