  "siblingNote": "silicon/iwakura/fuigo = the ELECTRONIC (digital ternary) silicon line; noroshi = the PHOTONIC (光電融合) sibling. tsutae = RF comms device; noroshi = optical comms chip. watatsuna = the submarine-cable medium; noroshi = the CPO transceiver chips at the cable's ends.",
